        "content": [
          "English is the only major language",
          "that kept both halves of its own",
          "conquest. Most of the time, when two",
          "languages collide, one of them wins.",
          "English refused to choose.",
          "",
          "begin / commence",
          "buy  / purchase",
          "end  / conclude",
          "help / assist",
          "ask  / enquire",
          "",
          "The Germanic word is the one you",
          "reach for first. The Norman word is",
          "the one you reach for when the room",
          "gets formal. Neither is better. The",
          "choice itself is the skill."
